title: Jazz Goldberg Variations - Stuttgart Chamber Orchestra, K&agrave
description:
This awesome jazz CD contains Bach's Goldberg Variations performed first in classic style by the Stuttgart Chamber Orchestra, then recomposed as a jazz interpretations by Kalman Olah and Mini Schulz.

The jazz versions are inordinately beautiful. And what's more, there are only two copies of this CD available in the world, retailing for $120 and up. (See: www (dot) amazon (dot) com/Goldberg-Variations-Johann-Sebastian-Bach/dp/B000056VBK

Want a sample? This is just gorgeous: www (dot) youtube (dot) com/watch?v=MCQ01pNaAVo


Highly recommended!
